entry.title: JKM Satin Bow With Twist Tie - 5/8"
entry.summary:
Vendor: JKM
Type: Bows
Price: 16.83

Satin Bow With Twist Tie is a ready made fabric satin bow 2 1/2" x 1 3/4" with a 5" long twist tie for easy attachment to any project. It is made of 5/8" single face satin (finished on one side) and is available in a great selection of colors. It comes in 100 bows per box of the same color.
(Product Characteristic: Bows) / (Fabric Content: 100% Polyester)
